  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Obtain information using a randomized treatment to assess the antidepressant and anxiolytic
      efficacy of divalproex vs. placebo for nonrefractory bipolar patients with major depressive
      episodes.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Study is 6 weeks long, with 7 clinical visits.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
